cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.SE 

The paper proposes a framework for evaluating security and robustness of machine learning systems, specifically computer vision systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, the paper also discusses machine learning techniques and safety properties, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper addresses security concerns, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and the implementation and evaluation of the proposed methodology could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering).
